<doc id="621171" wikidata="Q464260" url="?curid=621171" title="Saburo Ishikura">
<text>Saburo Ishikura (石倉 三郎 &quot;Ishikura Saburō&quot;, born December 16, 1946, in Kagawa, Japan) is a Japanese actor that has acted in several movies directed by Beat Takeshi. He has also appeared in a few of Takeshi&#x27;s recent films which include &quot;Zatoichi&quot; (2003) as Boss Ogi and &quot;Asakusa Kid&quot; (2002).

He has also made guest appearances in Gaki No Tsukai Batsu Games. Specifically 2008&#x27;s Newspaper Agency as a man in a oversize bag and 2009&#x27;s Hotel in a golf bag.

==Filmography==
===Film===
*&quot;Go! Go! Sakura Club&quot; (2023), Kikuo Hanada
*&quot;The Scoop&quot; (2024), Yamamoto
*&quot;Our Eternal Song&quot; (2025)

===Television=== 
*&quot;Aoi&quot; (2000), Aoyama Tadatoshi
*&quot;Boogie Woogie&quot; (2023), Kazuichi Jirōmaru

